[1.210, "o", "\r\n"]
[0.000, "o", "\u001b[1;34m══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[0.000, "o", "\u001b[1;34m  3. DISCOVER A PEER — fresh agent B publishes its Agent Card (npk/vpk + price)\u001b[0m\r\n"]
